Text:  'Well, then, you take it.
Audio: "'Well, then you take it.'

#:~:text=it.-,'%20
Text:  '
Audio: 

#:~:text=wendy%20had%20a%20s,.%20
Text:  Wendy had a splendid idea. 
Audio: "'Wendy had a splendid idea.

#:~:text='why%20n,%3F
Text:  'Why not both take it at the same time?
Audio: "'Why not both take it at the same time?'

#:~:text=me%3F-,'%20
Text:  '
Audio: 

#:~:text='ce,g.%20
Text:  'Certainly,' said Mr. Darling. 
Audio: "'Certainly,' said Mr. Darling.

#:~:text='are%20you%20r,%3F
Text:  'Are you ready, Michael?
Audio: "'Are you ready, Michael?'

#:~:text=ael%3F-,'%20
Text:  '
Audio: 

#:~:text=wendy%20ga,k.%20
Text:  Wendy gave the words, one, two, three, and Michael took his medicine, but Mr. Darling slipped his behind his back.
Audio: "'Wendy gave the words, one, two, three.' "'And Michael took his medicine, but Mr. Darling slipped his behind his back.

#:~:text=there%20was%20a%20y,!
Text:  There was a yell of rage from Michael, and 'O father!
Audio: "'There was a yell of rage from Michael, and—' "'Oh, father!'

#:~:text='%20wendy%20e,%20
Text:  ' Wendy exclaimed.
Audio: Wendy exclaimed.

#:~:text='what%20do%20,%3F
Text:  'What do you mean by "O father"?
Audio: "'What do you mean by, oh, father?'

#:~:text='%20mr.%20darling%20d,%20
Text:  ' Mr. Darling demanded. 
