#:~:text=i%20meant,.
Text:  I meant to take mine, but I—I missed it.
Audio: "'I meant to take mine, but I—' "'I missed it.'

#:~:text=it.-,'%20
Text:  '
Audio: 

#:~:text=it%20was%20dr,.%20
Text:  It was dreadful the way all the three were looking at him, just as if they did not admire him. 
Audio: "'It was dreadful the way all the three were looking at him, "'just as if they did not admire him.

#:~:text='look%20h,.%20
Text:  'Look here, all of you,' he said entreatingly, as soon as Nana had gone into the bathroom, 'I have just thought of a splendid joke. 
Audio: "'Look here, all of you,' he said, entreatingly, "'as soon as Nana had gone into the bathroom. "'I have just thought of a splendid joke.

#:~:text=i%20shall%20p,!
Text:  I shall pour my medicine into Nana's bowl, and she will drink it, thinking it is milk!
Audio: "'I shall pour my medicine into Nana's bowl, "'and she will drink it, thinking it is milk.'

#:~:text=ilk!-,'%20
Text:  '
Audio: 

#:~:text=it%20was%20the%20co,.%20
Text:  It was the colour of milk; but the children did not have their father's sense of humour, and they looked at him reproachfully as he poured the medicine into Nana's bowl. 
Audio: "'It was the colour of milk, "'but the children did not have their father's sense of humour, "'and they looked at him reproachfully "'as he poured the medicine into Nana's bowl.

#:~:text='what%20fun%2C,d.%20
Text:  'What fun,' he said doubtfully, and they did not dare expose him when Mrs. Darling and Nana returned.
Audio: "'What fun!' he said doubtfully. "'And they did not dare expose him "'when Mrs. Darling and Nana returned.

#:~:text='na,.
Text:  'Nana, good dog,' he said, patting her, 'I have put a little milk into your bowl, Nana.
Audio: "'Nana, good dog!' he said, patting her. "'I have put a little milk into your bowl, Nana.'

#:~:text=na.-,'%20
Text:  '
Audio: 

#:~:text=nana%20wag,.%20
Text:  Nana wagged her tail, ran to the medicine, and began lapping it. 
Audio: "'Nana wagged her tail, ran to the medicine, "'and began lapping it.

#:~:text=then%20she%20g,l.%20
Text:  Then she gave Mr. Darling such a look, not an angry look: she showed him the great red tear that makes us so sorry for noble dogs, and crept into her kennel.
Audio: "'Then she gave Mr. Darling such a look, "'not an angry look. "'She showed him the great red tear "'that makes us so sorry for noble dogs, "'and crept into her kennel.

#:~:text=mr.%20darling%20was%20frightfully%20a,.%20
Text:  Mr. Darling was frightfully ashamed of himself, but he would not give in. 
