Text:  'You don't think I would kill him while he was sleeping! 
Audio: YOU DON'T THINK I WOULD KILL HIM WHILE HE WAS SLEEPING

#:~:text=i%20would%20w,.%20
Text:  I would wake him first, and then kill him. 
Audio: I WOULD WAKE HIM FIRST AND THEN KILL HIM

#:~:text=that's%20the%20w,.
Text:  That's the way I always do.
Audio: THAT'S THE WAY I ALWAYS DO

#:~:text=do.-,'%20
Text:  '
Audio: 

#:~:text='i%20say!
Text:  'I say! 
