Audio: TONS

#:~:text=ons.-,'%20
Text:  '
Audio: 

#:~:text=john%20said%20',.%20
Text:  John said 'how ripping,' but decided to have tea first. 
Audio: JOHN SAID HOW RIPPING BUT DECIDED TO HAVE TEA FIRST

#:~:text=he%20asked%20i,.%20
Text:  He asked if there were many pirates on the island just now, and Peter said he had never known so many.
Audio: HE ASKED IF THERE WERE MANY PIRATES ON THE ISLAND JUST NOW AND PETER SAID HE HAD NEVER KNOWN SO MANY

#:~:text='who%20i,%3F
Text:  'Who is captain now?
Audio: WHO IS CAPTAIN NOW

#:~:text=ow%3F-,'%20
Text:  '
Audio: 

#:~:text='hook%2C,.%20
Text:  'Hook,' answered Peter; and his face became very stern as he said that hated word.
