Text:  Then indeed Michael began to cry, and even John could speak in gulps only, for they knew Hook's reputation.
Audio: THEN INDEED MICHAEL BEGAN TO CRY AND EVEN JOHN COULD SPEAK IN GULPS ONLY FOR THEY KNEW HOOK'S REPUTATION

#:~:text='he%20wa,.%20
