#:~:text='he%20is%20t,.%20
Text:  'He is the worst of them all. 
Audio: HE'S THE WORST OF THEM ALL

#:~:text=he%20is%20the%20o,.
Text:  He is the only man of whom Barbecue was afraid.
Audio: HE'S THE ONLY MAN OF WHOM BARBECUE WAS AFRAID

#:~:text=id.-,'%20
Text:  '
Audio: 

