Text:  'Yes, me,' said Peter sharply.
Audio: YES ME SAID PETER SHARPLY

#:~:text='i%20wasn't%20m,.
Text:  'I wasn't meaning to be disrespectful.
Audio: I WASN'T MEANING TO BE DISRESPECTFUL

#:~:text=ul.-,'%20
Text:  '
Audio: 

#:~:text='oh%2C%20a,'%20
Text:  'Oh, all right'
