#:~:text=the%20pirates%20d,.%20
Text:  The pirates disappeared among the trees, and in a moment their captain and Smee were alone. 
Audio: The pirates disappeared among the trees, and in a moment their captain and Smee were alone.

#:~:text=hook%20he,.%20
Text:  Hook heaved a heavy sigh; and I know not why it was, perhaps it was because of the soft beauty of the evening, but there came over him a desire to confide to his faithful bo'sun the story of his life. 
Audio: Hook heaved a heavy sigh, and I know not why it was. Perhaps it was because of the soft beauty of the evening. But there came over him a desire to confide to his faithful bosun the story of his life.

#:~:text=he%20spok,.%20
Text:  He spoke long and earnestly, but what it was all about Smee, who was rather stupid, did not know in the least.
Audio: He spoke long and earnestly, but what it was all about Smee, who was rather stupid, did not know in the least.

#:~:text=anon%20he%20c,.%20
Text:  Anon he caught the word Peter.
Audio: Anon he caught the word Peter.

#:~:text='mos,.%20
Text:  'Most of all,' Hook was saying passionately, 'I want their captain, Peter Pan. 
