Audio: He snatched the hat off John's head Knocked out the bottom And put the hat on the roof

#:~:text=the%20little%20house%20w,.%20
Text:  The little house was so pleased to have such a capital chimney that, as if to say thank you, smoke immediately began to come out of the hat.
Audio: The little house was so pleased to have such a capital chimney That, as if to say thank you, smoke immediately began to come out of the hat

#:~:text=now%20real,.%20
Text:  Now really and truly it was finished. 
Audio: Now, really and truly, it was finished

#:~:text=nothing%20r,.%20
