Audio: Nothing remained to do but to knock

#:~:text='all%20l,.
Text:  'All look your best,' Peter warned them; 'first impressions are awfully important.
Audio: All look your best, Peter warned them First impressions are awfully important

#:~:text=ant.-,'%20
Text:  '
