#:~:text=he%20was%20gl,.%20
Text:  He was glad no one asked him what first impressions are; they were all too busy looking their best.
Audio: He was glad no one asked him what first impressions are They were all too busy looking their best

#:~:text=he%20knocke,.%20
Text:  He knocked politely; and now the wood was as still as the children, not a sound to be heard except from Tinker Bell, who was watching from a branch and openly sneering.
Audio: He knocked politely And now the wood was as still as the children

#:~:text=what%20the%20b,%3F%20
Text:  What the boys were wondering was, would any one answer the knock? 
Audio: What the boys was wondering was Would anyone answer the knock?

#:~:text=if%20a%20l,%3F%20
Text:  If a lady, what would she be like?
Audio: If a lady, what would she be like?

