Audio: The door opened and a lady came out

#:~:text=it%20was%20wen,%20
Text:  It was Wendy. 
Audio: It was Wendy

#:~:text=they%20all%20wh,.%20
Text:  They all whipped off their hats.
Audio: They all whipped off their hats

#:~:text=she%20looked%20p,.%20
Text:  She looked properly surprised, and this was just how they had hoped she would look.
Audio: She looked properly surprised And this was just how they had hoped she would look

#:~:text='where%20a,%3F
Text:  'Where am I?
Audio: Where am I?

#:~:text='%20she%20said.
Text:  ' she said.
Audio: She said

#:~:text=of%20course%20sl,.%20
Text:  Of course Slightly was the first to get his word in. 
Audio: Of course, Slightly was the first to get his word in

#:~:text='wendy%20,.
Text:  'Wendy lady,' he said rapidly, 'for you we built this house.
Audio: Wendy, lady, he said rapidly For you, we built this house

#:~:text=se.-,'%20
Text:  '
Audio: 

#:~:text='oh%2C%20s,.%20
Text:  'Oh, say you're pleased,' cried Nibs.
Audio: Oh, say you're pleased, cried Nibs

#:~:text='lov,.%20
Text:  'Lovely, darling house,' Wendy said, and they were the very words they had hoped she would say.
Audio: Lovely, darling house Wendy said And they were the very words they had hoped she would say

#:~:text='and%20we,.%20
Text:  'And we are your children,' cried the twins.
Audio: And we are your children, cried the twins

