Audio: Ought I? Wendy

#:~:text='%20wendy%20said%2C%20al,.%20
Text:  ' Wendy said, all shining. 
Audio: Wendy said, all shining

#:~:text='of%20course%20it',.%20
Text:  'Of course it's frightfully fascinating, but you see I am only a little girl. 
Audio: Of course, it's frightfully fascinating But you see, I'm only a little girl I

#:~:text=i%20have%20no%20,.
Text:  I have no real experience.
Audio: I have no real experience

#:~:text=ce.-,'%20
Text:  '
Audio: 

