#:~:text=.%20-,'boat%20ahoy!
Text:  'Boat ahoy!
Audio: Boat ahoy,

#:~:text='%20ag,.%20
Text:  ' again came the cry.
Audio: again came the voice.

#:~:text=now%20wend,.%20
Text:  Now Wendy understood. 
Audio: Now Wendy understood.

#:~:text=the%20real%20h,.%20
Text:  The real Hook was also in the water.
Audio: The real Hook was also in the water.

#:~:text=he%20was%20sw,.%20
Text:  He was swimming to the boat, and as his men showed a light to guide him he had soon reached them. 
Audio: He was swimming to the boat, and as his men showed a light to guide him, he had soon reached them.

#:~:text=in%20the%20lig,.%20
Text:  In the light of the lantern Wendy saw his hook grip the boat's side; she saw his evil swarthy face as he rose dripping from the water, and, quaking, she would have liked to swim away, but Peter would not budge. 
Audio: In the light of the lantern, Wendy saw his hook grip the boat's side. She saw his evil swarthy face as he rose, dripping from the water, and, quaking, she would have liked to swim away, but Peter would not budge.

#:~:text=he%20was%20ti,.%20
Text:  He was tingling with life and also top-heavy with conceit. 
Audio: He was tingling with life, and also top-heavy with conceit.

#:~:text='am,!
Text:  'Am I not a wonder, oh, I am a wonder!
Audio: Am I not a wonder? Oh, I am a wonder,

#:~:text='%20he%20whispered%20t,.%20
Text:  ' he whispered to her; and though she thought so also, she was really glad for the sake of his reputation that no one heard him except herself.
Audio: he whispered to her, and though she thought so also, she was really glad for the sake of his reputation that no one heard him except himself.

#:~:text=he%20signed%20to%20h,.%20
Text:  He signed to her to listen.
Audio: He signed to her to listen.

#:~:text=the%20two%20pirates%20w,.%20
Text:  The two pirates were very curious to know what had brought their captain to them, but he sat with his head on his hook in a position of profound melancholy.
Audio: The two pirates were very curious to know what had brought their captain to them, but he sat with his head on his hook in a position of profound melancholy.

#:~:text='captain%2C%20,%3F
Text:  'Captain, is all well?
Audio: Captain, is all well? they

#:~:text='%20they%20as,.%20
Text:  ' they asked timidly, but he answered with a hollow moan.
