#:~:text='he%20sighs%2C,.%20
Text:  'He sighs,' said Smee.
Audio: He sighs, said Smee.

#:~:text='he%20sighs%20,.%20
Text:  'He sighs again,' said Starkey.
Audio: He sighs again, said Starkey.

#:~:text='and%20ye,.%20
Text:  'And yet a third time he sighs,' said Smee.
Audio: And yet a third time he sighs, said Smee.

#:~:text='what's%20u,%3F
Text:  'What's up, captain?
Audio: 

#:~:text=in%3F-,'%20
Text:  '
Audio: 

#:~:text=then%20at%20last%20he%20sp,.%20
Text:  Then at last he spoke passionately.
Audio: Then at last he spoke passionately.

#:~:text='the%20ga,.
Text:  'The game's up,' he cried, 'those boys have found a mother.
Audio: The game's up, he cried. Those boys have found a mother.

#:~:text=her.-,'%20
Text:  '
Audio: 

#:~:text=affrighted%20t,.%20
Text:  Affrighted though she was, Wendy swelled with pride.
Audio: Afrighted though she was, Wendy swelled with pride.

#:~:text='o%20e,.%20
Text:  'O evil day,' cried Starkey.
