#:~:text=it%20was%20the%20nes,.%20
Text:  It was the nest I have told you of, floating on the lagoon, and the Never bird was sitting on it.
Audio: It was the nest I have told you of, floating on the lagoon, and the never-bird was sitting on it.

#:~:text='see%2C,.%20
Text:  'See,' said Hook in answer to Smee's question, 'that is a mother. 
