#:~:text=smee%2C%20m,.
Text:  Smee, much impressed, gazed at the bird as the nest was borne past, but the more suspicious Starkey said, 'If she is a mother, perhaps she is hanging about here to help Peter.
Audio: Smee, much impressed, gazed at the bird as the nest was borne past. But the more suspicious Starkey said, If she's a mother, perhaps she's hanging about here to help Peter.

