#:~:text=%20me.-,'%20
Text:  '
Audio: 

#:~:text=he%20was%20ro,.%20
Text:  He was roused from this dejection by Smee's eager voice.
Audio: He was roused from this dejection by Smee's eager voice.

#:~:text='captain%2C',%3F
Text:  'Captain,' said Smee, 'could we not kidnap these boys' mother and make her our mother?
Audio: Captain, said Smee, could we not kidnap these boys' mother and make her our mother?

