#:~:text=he%20did%20t,.%20
Text:  He did this because there is a saying in the Neverland that, every time you breathe, a grown-up dies; and Peter was killing them off vindictively as fast as possible.
Audio: He did this because there is a saying in the Neverland that, every time you breathe, a grown-up dies, and Peter was killing them off, vindictively, as fast as possible.

