Audio: The cup was poisoned.

#:~:text='bes,.
Text:  'Besides,' said Peter, quite believing himself, 'I never fell asleep.
Audio: Besides, said Peter, quite believing himself, I never fell asleep.

#:~:text=leep.-,'%20
Text:  '
