#:~:text=no%20time%20for%20w,.%20
Text:  No time for words now; time for deeds; and with one of her lightning movements Tink got between his lips and the draught, and drained it to the dregs.
Audio: No time for words now, time for deeds. And with one of her lightning movements Tink got between his lips and the draught and drainedning it to the dregs.

#:~:text='why%2C,%3F
Text:  'Why, Tink, how dare you drink my medicine?
Audio: Why, Tink, how dare you drink my medicine?

#:~:text=ine%3F-,'%20
Text:  '
Audio: 

#:~:text=but%20she%20d,.%20
Text:  But she did not answer. 
Audio: But she did not answer.

#:~:text=already%20s,.%20
Text:  Already she was reeling in the air.
Audio: Already she was reeling in the air.

#:~:text='what%20is%20t,%3F
Text:  'What is the matter with you?
Audio: What is the matter with you?

#:~:text='%20cried%20peter%2C%20s,.%20
Text:  ' cried Peter, suddenly afraid.
Audio: cried Peter, suddenly afraid.

#:~:text='it%20was%20p,.
Text:  'It was poisoned, Peter,' she told him softly; 'and now I am going to be dead.
Audio: It was poisoned, Peter, she told him softly. And now I am going to be dead.

#:~:text=ad.-,'%20
Text:  '
Audio: 

#:~:text='o%20t,%3F
