#:~:text=hook%20had%20w,.%20
Text:  Hook had well-nigh forgotten his prisoners, but as he swung round on them now his face lit up again.
Audio: Hook had well nigh forgotten his prisoners, but as he swung round on them now, his face licked up again.

#:~:text='lads%2C'%20he%20c,.%20
Text:  'Lads,' he cried to his crew, 'here's a notion. 
Audio: But, lads, he cried to his crew, now here's a notion.

#:~:text=open%20t,.%20
Text:  Open the cabin door and drive them in. 
Audio: Open the cabin door and drive them in.

#:~:text=let%20them%20fi,.%20
Text:  Let them fight the doodle-doo for their lives. 
Audio: Let them fight the doodledoo for their lives.

#:~:text=if%20they%20k,.
Text:  If they kill him, we're so much the better; if he kills them, we're none the worse.
Audio: If they kill him, we're so much the better. If he kills them, we're none the worse.

#:~:text=se.-,'%20
Text:  '
Audio: 

#:~:text=for%20the%20l,.%20
Text:  For the last time his dogs admired Hook, and devotedly they did his bidding. 
