Audio: Fling the girl overboard, cried Hook, and they made a rush at the figure in the cloak.

#:~:text='there's%20n,.%20
Text:  'There's none can save you now, missy,' Mullins hissed jeeringly.
Audio: This nun can save you now, missy, Mullins hissed jeeringly.

