Audio: Nana, I dreamt my dear ones had come back.

#:~:text=nana%20h,.%20
Text:  Nana had filmy eyes, but all she could do was to put her paw gently on her mistress's lap; and they were sitting together thus when the kennel was brought back. 
Audio: Nana had filmy eyes, but all she could do was put her paw gently on her mistress's lap, and they were sitting together thus, when the kennel was brought back.

#:~:text=as%20mr,.%20
Text:  As Mr. Darling puts his head out at it to kiss his wife, we see that his face is more worn than of yore, but has a softer expression.
Audio: As Mr. Darling put his head out to kiss his wife, we see that his face is more worn than of yore, but has a softer expression.

#:~:text=he%20gave%20h,.%20
Text:  He gave his hat to Liza, who took it scornfully; for she had no imagination, and was quite incapable of understanding the motives of such a man. 
Audio: He gave his hat to Liza, who took it scornfully. She had no imagination, and was quite incapable of understanding the motives of such a man.

#:~:text=outs,.%20
Text:  Outside, the crowd who had accompanied the cab home were still cheering, and he was naturally not unmoved.
Audio: Outside, the crowd who had accompanied the cab home were still cheering, and he was naturally not unmoved.

#:~:text='li,.
Text:  'Listen to them,' he said; 'it is very gratifying.
