#:~:text='lo,.%20
Text:  'Lot of little boys,' sneered Liza.
Audio: Lots of little boys, sneered Liza.

#:~:text='there%20w,.%20
Text:  'There were several adults to-day,' he assured her with a faint flush; but when she tossed her head he had not a word of reproof for her. 
Audio: There were several adults to-day, he assured her with a faint flush, but when she tossed her head he had not a word of reproof for her.

#:~:text=socia,.%20
Text:  Social success had not spoilt him; it had made him sweeter. 
Audio: Social success had not spoiled him. It had made him sweeter. For

#:~:text=for%20so,t.%20
Text:  For some time he sat half out of the kennel, talking with Mrs. Darling of this success, and pressing her hand reassuringly when she said she hoped his head would not be turned by it.
Audio: For some time he sat with his head out of the kennel, talking with Mrs. Darling of this success, and pressing her hand reassuringly when she said she hoped his head would not be turned by it.

