Audio: We have ridden it so, because that was the charming arrangement planned by them before we left the ship. But something must have happened since then. For it is not they who have flown in. It is Peter and Tinkerbell.

#:~:text=peter's%20f,.%20
Text:  Peter's first words tell all.
