#:~:text=now%20i%20,.%20
Text:  Now I understand what had hitherto puzzled me, why when Peter had exterminated the pirates he did not return to the island and leave Tink to escort the children to the mainland. 
Audio: Now I understand what had hitherto puzzled me. Why, when Peter had exterminated the pirates he did not return to the island and leave Tink to escort the children to the mainland.

#:~:text=this%20tr,.%20
Text:  This trick had been in his head all the time.
Audio: This trick had been in his head all the time.

#:~:text=instead%20of%20f,.%20
Text:  Instead of feeling that he was behaving badly he danced with glee; then he peeped into the day-nursery to see who was playing. 
