Text:  She is a pretty lady, but not so pretty as my mother. 
Audio: She is a pretty lady, but not so pretty as my mother.

#:~:text=her%20mouth%20,.
Text:  Her mouth is full of thimbles, but not so full as my mother's was.
Audio: Her mouth is full of thimbles, but not so full as my mother's was.

#:~:text=as.-,'%20
Text:  '
