Text:  He peeped in again to see why the music had stopped; and now he saw that Mrs. Darling had laid her head on the box, and that two tears were sitting on her eyes.
Audio: He peeped in again to see why the music had stopped, and now he saw that Mrs. Darling had laid her head on the box, and that two tears were sitting on her eyes.

#:~:text='she%20w,.'%20
Text:  'She wants me to unbar the window,' thought Peter, 'but I won't, not I.'
