#:~:text='come%20o,.%20
Text:  'Come on, Tink,' he cried, with a frightful sneer at the laws of nature; 'we don't want any silly mothers'; and he flew away.
Audio: Come on, Tink! he cried, with a frightful sneer at the laws of nature. We don't want any silly mothers. And he flew away.

