#:~:text=there%20c,.%20
Text:  There could not have been a lovelier sight; but there was none to see it except a strange boy who was staring in at the window. 
Audio: There could not have been a lovelier sight, but there was none to see it except a little boy who was staring in at the window.

#:~:text=he%20had%20e,.%20
Text:  He had ecstasies innumerable that other children can never know; but he was looking through the window at the one joy from which he must be for ever barred.
