#:~:text=she%20was%20one,.%20
Text:  She was one of the kind that likes to grow up. 
Audio: She was one of the kind that likes to grow up.

#:~:text=in%20the%20end%20s,.%20
Text:  In the end she grew up of her own free will a day quicker than other girls.
Audio: In the end she grew up of her own free will a day quicker than other girls.

#:~:text=all%20the%20boys%20wer,.%20
Text:  All the boys were grown up and done for by this time; so it is scarcely worth while saying anything more about them. 
Audio: All the boys were grown up and done for by this time. So it is scarcely worthwhile saying anything more about them.

#:~:text=you%20may%20see%20t,.%20
Text:  You may see the twins and Nibs and Curly any day going to an office, each carrying a little bag and an umbrella. 
Audio: You may see the twins and Nibs and Curly any day going to an office, each carrying a little bag and an umbrella.

#:~:text=michael%20i,.%20
Text:  Michael is an engine-driver. 
Audio: Michael is an engine driver,

#:~:text=slightly%20ma,.%20
